creator: African Puzzle
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to African Puzzle WORKS,
The mobile application partnering with you and your business to assist you in all your tasks!

African Puzzle WORKS is a simple and practical mobile application, designed for professionals: craftsmen, freelancers, creatives.

It helps you to better organize your work, remember everything and efficiently combines voice, photo and text features. In short, a second brain in your pocket!

PERSONALIZE YOUR CLIENT INFORMATION EASILY:
- Import your contacts with a simple click
- Quickly create, modify, and save your customer information
- Access your customer information quickly

FIND ALL YOUR CUSTOMERS’ PROJECTS IN ONE PLACE
- Create your projects by recording voice notes, attaching photos or adding text notes
- Associate your projects with your clients
- Follow your projects in real time

ORGANIZE YOUR APPOINTMENTS AND RECEIVE NOTIFICATIONS:
- Find your appointments quickly
- Define the frequency of your notifications
- Manage your schedule and meet your important deadlines

COLLECT EXAMPLES OF YOUR CREATIONS IN AN ALBUM:
- Organize the categories to easily present to your clients
- Find photos of your achievements that customers have liked

FOLLOW YOUR BUDGETS AND REVENUES:
- Track and review the deposits and payments received from customers
- Follow your business performance and maintain piece of mind

African Puzzle WORKS is an application developed by African Puzzle.
descriptionShort: The mobile application that assists you with your projects or business!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Lots of bug fixes and visual improvements including:
⁃ 👓 Making text in Project List cards easier to read
⁃ 🗓 Allowing due dates into 2022 and beyond
⁃ ♻ Preventing auto log out so no need to sign in every time
